            "distance": 3.1,
            "stagger_seconds": 0.9
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The floor remembers every pick that broke it \u2014 pressure finds the old wounds and the air rushes inward like a held breath finally released. What stands in that circle learns what the stone already knows about giving way."
    },
